data.description: This gorgeous 3br/2ba home is ready to wow you! Tucked into the crook of Acorn Park and featuring a generous .65 ac lot, this is truly your retreat in the city. Large windows and sun-fulled 3-season porch keep this home feeling light and bright. Kitchen is. full of upgrades with stainless appliances and oak cabinets. New floors, fresh paint. Lower level family room provides additional room for entertaining, while the utility room offers tons of storage space! Conveniently located one block from County Rd C and Rice.
